Titolo: Xanagrams

Anno: 1984

Descrizione: Xanagrams is an educational game that is a cross between a crossword puzzle and Scrabble. It was given away for free with the Amstrad CPC 464 and was a popular game. There are 3 difficulty level to the game, from middle school aged to adults. A game can consist of 1-5 words and the player is given a jumble of letters to sort out to form the correct words.

Genere: Educational 

Valutazione: N/A
